{"tid":2337303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美艦現身南沙群島 中方抗議","createTime":"2020-12-23T07:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T10:11:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"58561f846cdc173aa31ef5fabb643a77c6e1d992","tid":2337303,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/CB547CBMERHPTB7PJ44CLUWOKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FCB547CBMERHPTB7PJ44CLUWOKE%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=1333fdee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FCB547CBMERHPTB7PJ44CLUWOKE%2F&h=58b5ec4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/CB547CBMERHPTB7PJ44CLUWOKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美艦現身南沙群島 中方抗議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OUCNLh1dmVaXhXk7ByBdlsWAZw8=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4CIQQTGQBARHEK4MODO7NORQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOUCNLh1dmVaXhXk7ByBdlsWAZw8%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4CIQQTGQBARHEK4MODO7NORQQ.jpg&h=914ed162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美軍麥凱恩號驅逐艦。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n中美軍事矛盾與日俱增，美軍馬斯廷號驅逐艦上周五（18日）穿越台灣海峽後，麥凱恩號（USS John S. McCain）驅逐艦昨現身南沙群島，引發中國政府不滿。解放軍批評美方侵犯中國主權和安全，同時表示堅決反對。美國國防部反駁，外國軍艦在南沙群島有航行自由。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍南部戰區新聞發言人田軍里空軍大校表示，12月22。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國第七艦隊回應，麥凱恩號根。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料華未來20年增94戰艦<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國會研究部近日報告引述美國國防部資料，指目前中國海軍戰艦共333艘，美軍戰艦共296艘，比中國少37艘。報告預測，到2040年的20年間，中國還會增加四艘航空母艦、六艘彈道導彈潛艇、十艘攻擊用核潛艇等94艘戰艦。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/環球網"},{"pid":"ff7c08a7110261e91d66a99d4d7516168b65ae28","tid":2337303,"uid":12171,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,